# Icon Branding Standard

- Use `warrior_icon.ico` as the only application icon for this repository.
- Treat `branding/master-icon.png` as the source image of truth.
- Before release packaging, run `./update-app-icon.ps1` to regenerate `warrior_icon.ico` from the source image.
- Keep project and installer references pointed to `warrior_icon.ico` (for example `ApplicationIcon`, installer setup icon, and shortcut icon fields).
- **Apply this icon to all applications in this repo and any future applications** unless the user explicitly instructs otherwise.
- Do not introduce alternate icons unless the user explicitly instructs otherwise.
